Gift version 0.04
=================

INSTALLATION

To install this module just do:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

No dependencies.
This module uses a standalone parser that was built using Parse::Yapp.
It does not require Parse::Yapp to work. 

